## Naming Conventions

| Type          | Convention                  | Example                         |
| ------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Route folders | kebab-case                  | `code-review/`, `chat-history/` |
| Components    | PascalCase                  | `ChatMessage.tsx`               |
| Hooks         | camelCase + `use` prefix    | `useChatHistory.ts`             |
| Schemas       | camelCase + `Schema` suffix | `reviewSchema`                  |
| Services      | camelCase + feature         | `chat.service.ts`               |
| Actions       | camelCase + `Action` suffix | `saveReviewAction`              |
| Constants     | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE        | `MAX_TOKENS`, `DEFAULT_LOCALE`  |
| Types files   | camelCase + `.d.ts`         | `chat.d.ts`                     |
| AI prompts    | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE        | `MENTOR_SYSTEM_PROMPT`          |

